%div#about-header
  .row
    %h1 Applications are built for people, and so are we.
    %h2 We take the stress out of building web and mobile applications by blowing up the black box. Watching your idea develop into a valuable application should be rewarding and informative, not daunting, and our methodologies make you an integral part of the process.
%div#principles
  .row
    .column.four
      #circle-white
      #tech-craft-icon
      %h5 Technical craft
      %h6 We have the tools, and we know how to use them. We build powerfully simple software
    .column.four
      #circle-white
      #creative-icon
      %h5 Creative design
      %h6 Great design means more than looking pretty, but your software will be the hottest in town
    .column.four
      #circle-white
      #user-centered-icon
      %h5 User-centered development
      %h6 You know your customers, and we know how people use technology

%div#expertise
  #expertise-text.row
    %h3 Cross-Disciplinary Digital Expertise
    %h4 We combine a design-oriented approach with technical and commercial expertise and strategic decision-making. We've got years of experience in everything involved with planning, designing, building and shipping digital products. We know our stuff.

%div#services
  .row
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #web-app-icon
        %h5 Web Applications
      %h6 Do you have an idea that will make or save money? If your product is your business then let's build an application that meets your needs, perfectly.
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #mobile-app-icon
        %h5 Mobile Applications
      %h6 Customers are on the go, and so is their technology. We make software that is as mobile as the people who use it.
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #scalability-icon
        %h5 Scalability
      %h6 Growing pains mean traction, but they don't have to hurt. You can't afford to lose customers due to poorly implemented code, and we won't let you.
  .row
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #testing-icon
        %h5 Testing
      %h6 Stories are nice, but learning through data is what strokes our geek. We track, analyze and learn as we build simply perfect software
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #lean-tactics-icon
        %h5 Lean Tactics
      %h6 Why guess when you can know? Lean tactics ensure we build the right application, every time, by adapting to new information gleaned through testing.
    .column.four
      #icon-text-row
        #agile-methodologies-icon
        %h5 Agile Methodologies
      %h6 We will work together to uncover the most pressing needs of your users before writing one line of code, and ensure our work serves the end goal, not to project plan as dictated on day one.

