  .row#team-row
    - @coshx_folks[6..11].each do |person, a|
      .column.two
        = render "team_member", :person => person
%div#how-we-work
  .row
    #circle-white
    #down-triangle  
  .row#work-header
    %h3 How We Work
    %h4 Our working process is highly iterative and built specifically for agile and responsive digital development. That means tight collaboration, streamlined projects, and better results.
  .row#step-even
    .column.one
    .column.four
      #circle-off-white
      #meet-icon
    .column.eight
      %h5 Pleased to Meet You
      %h4 Our vision matters most, and we want to learn about it while getting to know you and your business needs. We are not faceless mercenaries, but a talented team of superheroes that wants to help our clients succeed. Let’s make sure we are the right fit before taking this journey together.
  .row#step-odd
    .column.two
    .column.six
      %h5 Planning Session
      %h4 Your idea is the center of this energetic process, where we will sketch your application before writing one line of code. Furious whiteboarding and challenged ideas will generate a set of user stories, which are your entire application in written form. We will use these to prioritize your needs, estimate your cost and get cracking on the code.
    .column.four
      #circle-off-white
      #planning-icon
  .row#step-even
    .column.one
    .column.four
      #circle-off-white
      #design-icon
    .column.eight
      %h5 Design
      %h4 Design is where form and function meet. Tools are only as powerful as one’s ability to use them, and we will work together to design intuitive, powerfully simple applications. Our designers are artists, and our developers are craftsmen. Your software will look as good as it feels, solving problems along the way.
  .row#step-odd
    .column.two
    .column.six
      %h5 Minimum Viable Product
      %h4 Everything comes together in your Minimum Viable Product. We will get this into the hands of users in order to learn from their interactions and the data they generate. This saves you money by taking the guesswork out of development. We will crunch the numbers and sweat the technical details so you can focus on the fun stuff.
    .column.four
      #circle-off-white
      #mvp-icon
  .row#step-even
    .column.one
    .column.four
      #circle-off-white
      #iterate-icon
    .column.eight
      %h5 Iterate
      %h4 You have users, revenue and an appetite for more. Lessons learned will be turned into improved functionality and a better, stronger application, capturing more users along the way. Perhaps you are ready to hire your own tech team, and we will proudly hand you off like parents at the first day of school…but you will always have a room in our house.